<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 section-heading">
    <h1>Recent Highlights</h1>
    
  </div>
  <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
    

    
    
      <div class="card experience course">
        <div class="card-body"><h4 class="card-title exp-title text-muted my-0">NSF CAREER: NIC-Accelerated Active Messaging as a Generic Replacement and Awards for RDMA</h4><div class="card-subtitle my-0 article-metadata">NSF<span class="middot-divider"></span>

            
              2020
              
            
          </div>

          
            <div class="card-text">This proposal aims to fundamentally rethink the
design of server-side networking and develop new networking
abstractions for Network Interface Card (NIC) accelerated messaging.</div>
          

          
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <div class="card experience course">
        <div class="card-body"><h4 class="card-title exp-title text-muted my-0">NSF CRII: NeTS: Rethinking Flow Control for Cloud Data Center Networks</h4><div class="card-subtitle my-0 article-metadata">NSF<span class="middot-divider"></span>

            
              2019
              
            
          </div>

          
            <div class="card-text">This proposal makes the case for fundamentally
rethinking how queuing and flow control are performed in both physical
and virtual switches.</div>
          

          
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <div class="card experience course">
        <div class="card-body"><a href="https://research.google/outreach/faculty-research-awards/recipients/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><h4 class="card-title exp-title text-muted my-0">Google Faculty Research Award</h4></a><div class="card-subtitle my-0 article-metadata">Google<span class="middot-divider"></span>

            
